rt forms including Kenpo karate, Aikido, Judo and Muay Thai. Professor Rodriguez teaches workshops, self-defense seminars, and has previously worked in law enforcement. &nbsp;Professor Rodriguez actively coaches students in preparation for BJJ tournaments and MMA bouts and still competes in many Brazilian jiu-jitsu tournaments.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"67\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"49\"],\"staffName\":\"Gerardo Mulas\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Certified Personal Trainer, Yoga\",\"body\":\"<p>Gerardo Mulas is a certified personal trainer, yoga and martial arts expert whose mission is educating students the benefits of fitness and health and wellness goals. Gerardo specializes in sports performance, weight loss, injury rehabilitation, stress relief, nutritional counseling and meal planning. Gerardo has over two decades of professional and collegiate athletics under his belt, along with extensive training in kickboxing, boxing and grappling.<\\/p>\"}},\"68\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"50\"],\"staffName\":\"Randy Stem\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, fitness trainer \",\"body\":\"<p>Randy Stem is a 5th degree black belt trained in Karate, Kickboxing, and Judo and currently in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. Randy studied under the teachings of Allen Steen, widely recognized as the \'Father of American Taekwondo\', and has over 45 years of experience mastering martial arts. Randy strongly encourages his students to build a firm foundation in martial arts early on by focusing on the development of basic fundamental motor skills and concepts.<\\/p>\"}},\"69\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"43\"],\"staffName\":\"Sovandy Om\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Sovandy Om is a 5th degree black belt, kickboxing fitness certified trainer and a FPMA student favorite. Master Om has trained extensively in Tae Kwon Do, MMA, Gymnastic, as well as Crossfit. Along with a passion for martial arts, Master Om has an even bigger passion for fitness. Master Om works tirelessly with helping the students execute proper technique to achieve the maximum benefits, as well as helping students reach and exceed their fitness goals.<\\/p>\"}},\"70\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"46\"],\"staffName\":\"Alex Garcia\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Alex Garcia is a 2nd degree black belt in Tae Kwon Do who gravitated towards the world of martial arts at the age of 4. Alex soon began training to develop and perfect his skills for martial arts and became a student at Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts at the age of 10. Within 2 years, Alex\\u2019s dedication transformed him into an avid competitor, in which Alex received several 1st place wins in state martial arts championships.<\\/p>\"}},\"71\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"45\"],\"staffName\":\"Nathan Bagby\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt, Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Nathanael \\u201cNathan\\u201d Bagby is a 3rd degree black belt and an accomplished Muay Thai fighter and instructor. Nathan first became interested and started training in martial arts at the age of 8, and in the past 25 years, has trained in Isshinryu Karate, Eskrima, Tae Kwon Do, American Kickboxing, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, Close Quarter Combat, Boxing, and Muay Thai. &nbsp;Nathan has gone on to compete in several amateur and professional kickboxing and Muay Thai bouts.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"72\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\",\"staffName\":\"Mike Rose\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt \",\"body\":\"<p>Mike Rose has over 25 years of martial arts training, competition, and teaching experience in both Judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. Mike started training in Judo in 1992, when he received his black belt. In 1998, under the teachings of Greg Nelson, Mike began training in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and received his blue belt in 1999 and his black belt in 2009.<\\/p>\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-11 03:22:05', '2016-06-11 03:22:05', '20bea140-2c48-4f72-b9ec-c7c4cf650849'),
