 ('62', '33', '3', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Specials\",\"slug\":\"specials\",\"postDate\":1458879720,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"55\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Specials\",\"body\":\"<p>We pride ourselves in offering superior service and training for parents and kids. Outside of our extensive martial arts programs offered at both of our Dallas locations, FPMA offers various extra personal services that are very educational, affordable and definitely FUN! From private birthday celebrations to women\\u2019s self-defense classes, there\\u2019s a special FPMA Extra for everyone.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"40\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"56\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Parent\\u2019s Nights Out\",\"body\":\"<p>Got a date night or hang out with the crew night planned and need somewhere to take the kiddos? Bring \\u2018em to FPMA for Parents Night Out (PNO). The PNO program is on specified Saturdays from 5-9pm and welcomes both FPMA students and non-members to join in on a night full of pizza, movies, prizes and fun. <strong><em>Oh, did we mention Nerf gun wars, too?<\\/em><\\/strong> Just give one of our locations a call for more information, pricing and dates for the next PNO.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"57\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Birthday Parties\",\"body\":\"<p>Celebrate the birthday for your little martial artists Freddie Poole style! FPMA offers a personal experience with one of our many skilled instructors, ready to teach all of the little partiers some exciting new martial arts moves and put a unique spin on a birthday celebrations. Decorations, music and food are welcome. Intereste