 ('99', '17', '3', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Juniors\",\"slug\":\"juniors\",\"postDate\":1458100080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"79\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Juniors\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Juniors: (7 to 12 years old)&nbsp;<br><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts\\u00ae&nbsp;junior martial arts program&nbsp;is a unique training system that combines traditional values and principles with a modern system of combat, self-defense and fitness. Our exclusive system and program is a hybrid style, which incorporates training methods of karate and tae-kwon-do with westernized boxing, judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. FPMA has a variety of instructors teaching our program. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from different perspectives, which enhances the quality of training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"80\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our Juniors program focuses on advancement and growth based on each child\\u2019s individual pace. The key to our success is each discipline is introduced in stages to the student, rather than front-loading a program. Juniors will begin to grasp the concept of self-discipline as they achieve goals. When he\\/she tackles more difficult goals, the self-confidence grows and serves as a strong foundation in all aspects of life.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"22\":\"Juniors (7 -12 YO)\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-27 01:19:33', '2016-06-27 01:19:33', '67dd8401-628c-42e8-873a-c4478d6e43b1'),
 ('100', '81', '3', '1', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"slug\":\"brazilian-jiu-jitsu\",\"postDate\":1465960800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"82\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu: (7 to 12-year-old + Adults)&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The sport of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu can be quite complex. Our intro program helps break down all the essential concepts of the sport making it much easier to pick up for anybody. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial arts is a proud affiliate of the Carlos Machado BJJ association and network. Carlos Machado is nephew to one of the founders of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, late master Carlos Gracie. Carlos is determined to keep the legacy going through teaching and partnering with others including our very own, Freddie Poole.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"83\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our classes are curriculum oriented, providing a fast paced yet easy approach to learning Brazilian Jiu Jitsu for children (7-12 years of age) and adults. Students achieve great results in a short amount of time learning realistic skills great for both self-defense and increasing fitness and stamina. Students also learn strategies for advancing in rank after completing time and skill requirements, all in a fun and safe environment.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}},\"84\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kids BJJ Program\",\"body\":\"<p>The FPMA Brazilian Jiu Jitsu kids program is the perfect tool to change your child\\u2019s life forever. Lessons learned both on and off the mat will instill in them a confidence and self-belief that will continue with them throughout their lives. Plus, it\\u2019s FUN! FPMA stands firm on our anti-bullying policies, which have been reverse engineered to safely and effectively repel any aggressor, with truly phenomenal results.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Overall, the Kids BBJ program is designed to develop a sense of discipline, determination, leadership, commitment, responsibility, good sportsmanship and confidence into our future leaders<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"85\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Adults BJJ Fundamentals\",\"body\":\"<p>FPMA BJJ Fundamentals Program is designed to teach the overall self-defense strategy of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. The class begins with a pre-workout involving many body weight exercises and it will teach you the basics, from learning how to fall, to clinching, taking down and successfully setting up and applying a submission hold as well as various escapes. We provide a detailed instruction in wrestling, judo, and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, as they are all relevant to mastership. The class ends with positional training that helps students focus on the lesson of the week and get a feel for live training. Through repetition techniques, your training will slowly prepare you to begin drilling at a full resistance.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"22\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-27 01:20:02', '2016-06-27 01:20:02', 'c4f6cb7d-d4da-469c-a717-11acd8b4ba0d'),
 ('101', '86', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"slug\":\"ladies-kickboxing\",\"postDate\":1465960920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"87\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"body\":\"<p>The Ladies Kickboxing program is exclusively for ladies looking to combine an intense physical workout with the added perk of self-defense practices. Outside of incorporating various types of kickboxing techniques and strikes, FPMA Ladies kickboxing helps to educate students on many aspects of weight training, physical conditioning and yoga.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"]}},\"88\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>As intimidating as it may sound, kickboxing is perfect for all ladies. From beginners to experts, you\\u2019re sure to get the most from the&nbsp;private like atmosphere and pace of the class. With a dedicated staff of skilled professionals, kickboxing is the ideal workout option for mothers looking for an alternative to going to the gym and unique workout options with morning, afternoon and evening classes available.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"22\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-27 01:21:51', '2016-06-27 01:21:51', 'f3384a6b-80fa-4116-831b-1011aa33ca21'),
