 ('146', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1457804906,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"15\":{\"type\":\"homeHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kick. Punch. Learn.\",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts\\u00ae offers an exclusive hybrid training system that incorporates the traditional training values and principles of karate and tae-kwon-do with a contemporary system of combat, self-defense and fitness.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"10\"],\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"slides\":[\"125\",\"126\",\"127\"]}},\"18\":{\"type\":\"homePrograms\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Approach\",\"body\":\"<p>The key to our success is each discipline being introduced in stages to our student, rather than a front-loading program. This methodical approach ensures students are learning and mastering techniques at the highest level, as opposed to just going through motions. Additionally, we have a variety of skilled instructors teaching our programs. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from varied perspectives, which enhances the quality of the training. Each instructor at FPMA\\u00ae is trained to recognize a student\\u2019s personality, learning style, and individual needs.<\\/p>\",\"programs\":[\"16\",\"17\",\"81\",\"86\",\"89\",\"93\",\"96\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"102\"]}},\"52\":{\"type\":\"homeLocations\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Locations\",\"body\":\"<p>We currently have 2 locations to serve you.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"101\"]}},\"53\":{\"type\":\"twoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"bodyLeft\":\"<p>Come see for yourself why our martial arts system has been so popular for so many years. Our black belt instructors are here to help you achieve all your marital art and fitness goals.<\\/p>\",\"bodyRight\":\"\",\"columnsLeft\":\"col-3-of-5\",\"columnsRight\":\"col-2-of-5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"9\"],\"contactButton\":\"1\"}}}}}', '2016-07-12 14:37:32', '2016-07-12 14:37:32', '0f3615bc-be53-4578-89c5-17d9e897903a'),
 ('147', '128', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"About Us\",\"slug\":\"about-us-1\",\"postDate\":1468463564,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:32:44', '2016-07-14 02:32:44', '45d78f57-47b0-42a1-8667-7d2622bf9088'),
 ('148', '128', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"FPMA\",\"slug\":\"about-us-1\",\"postDate\":1468463520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"129\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:33:03', '2016-07-14 02:33:03', 'e79da5f1-51a1-4d97-a3b7-974a2b0fd1d4'),
 ('149', '73', '3', '1', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Freddie Poole\",\"slug\":\"about-freddie\",\"postDate\":1465959360,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"75\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"About Freddie\",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole began martial arts training in 1981, at the age of seven years old. He began studying at Southwest Karate Academy under Demetrius \\u201cGolden Greek\\u201d Havanas. Southwest Karate Academy produced some of the best martial arts champions and competitors in the world, at that time. The 80\\u2019s were the tail end of the \\u201cTexas Blood and Guts\\u201d era of martial arts. The lineage began with Jhoon Rhee and his first black belt was Allen Steen. Steen went on to train many black belts and students and Texas was known for producing some of the best fighters in the country. Tim Kirby, Billye Jackson, Raymond McCallum, Santae Wilson Jr. and Cliff Thomas were some of the world-class competitors who had influence over Poole\\u2019s training and development.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"119\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"76\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<h3>As a young brown belt, Poole began teaching at Sun Belt Karate Academy by assisting younger and lower ranking students with warm-ups, kick punch technique and forms. It was not uncommon to see Poole leading an adult class at 12 years old.<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole received his 1st degree black belt in 1986, under Tim Kirby, Billye Jackson and Raymond McCallum. Poole competed in the AOK and was a top ranked competitor in forms and fighting for many years as a junior competitor.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole began training with long time friend and kickboxing champion Guy Mezger in 1993. Poole began honing his boxing and kickboxing skills with Mezger, Billye Jackson, Santae Wilson Jr. and Coach Charles Brown and went on to win a national title in 1997, which earned a spot on the US National Kickboxing team.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole\\u2019s boxing experience comes from training with some of the best coaches in the business. Phil Sawyer and Olympic Boxing Bronze medalist Charles Brown have influenced Poole in his boxing training, as well as Golden Gloves Champion Alex Andrade.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole has several years of Muay Thai experience, training with Francisco Sanchez of New World Combat, as well as World Muay Thai champion and MMA veteran Pete Spratt and Muay Thai champion Jason House.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole\\u2019s Judo experience comes from training with Master Vince Tamura and Judo Black Belt Rico Castro.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole currently trains under the tutelage of 8th degree Brazilian Jiu Jitsu master, Carlos Machado, where he holds a brown belt and is a proud affiliate of Machado Jiu Jitsu. Poole has also trained with many talented Brazilian Jiu Jitsu black belts including Kenny McClure, Jeff Sawyer, Rico Castro and Taryn Douglas.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole has competed all over the United States and internationally in Europe, winning a KICK International title in 2004 along with many team karate titles from 1999-2004. Poole also fought for Team Texas in Chuck Norris\\u2019s televised fight league, The World Combat League.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole has taken his vast knowledge of martial arts and created a well-rounded training system for all ages. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts is the most balanced martial arts training system, combining traditional training elements with practical real world application. By integrating both of these elements into one system, one can truly train in mixed martial arts.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Since opening its doors in 2004, Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has been impacting thousands&nbsp;of&nbsp;lives in the community. Our friendly staff looks forward each day to helping our students achieve their goals. Although standards are set high, each student at FPMA is evaluated on an individual basis to ensure progression on their own timeline. This approach ensures students achieve and&nbsp;earn rank on their own merit.&nbsp;We encourage our students to trust the process and enjoy it. Earning a black belt at FPMA is a once in a lifetime experience!<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:34:57', '2016-07-14 02:34:57', 'a5ef50ec-a06d-49c0-87f8-266bf84aa6f8'),
 ('150', '128', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"FPMA\",\"slug\":\"about-us-1\",\"postDate\":1468463520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"129\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Since opening its doors in 2004, Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has been impacting thousands of lives in the community. Our friendly staff looks forward each day to helping our students achieve their goals.\",\"body\":\"<p>Although standards are set high, each student at FPMA is evaluated on an individual basis to ensure progression on their own timeline. This approach ensures students achieve and&nbsp;earn rank on their own merit.&nbsp;We encourage our students to trust the process and enjoy it. Earning a black belt at FPMA is a once in a lifetime experience! The dedicated team of instructors at FPMA have taken their experience of martial arts and created a well-rounded training system for all ages. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts is the most balanced martial arts training system, combining traditional training elements with practical real world application. By integrating both of these elements into one system, one can truly train in mixed martial arts.<br><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:36:07', '2016-07-14 02:36:07', '50b6b4b7-0c75-465a-9239-bf79914419a5'),
 ('151', '73', '3', '1', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Freddie Poole\",\"slug\":\"about-freddie\",\"postDate\":1465959360,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"75\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"About Freddie\",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole began martial arts training in 1981, at the age of seven years old. He began studying at Southwest Karate Academy under Demetrius \\u201cGolden Greek\\u201d Havanas. Southwest Karate Academy produced some of the best martial arts champions and competitors in the world, at that time. The 80\\u2019s were the tail end of the \\u201cTexas Blood and Guts\\u201d era of martial arts. The lineage began with Jhoon Rhee and his first black belt was Allen Steen. Steen went on to train many black belts and students and Texas was known for producing some of the best fighters in the country. Tim Kirby, Billye Jackson, Raymond McCallum, and Santae Wilson Jr.&nbsp; were some of the world-class competitors who had influence over Poole\\u2019s training and development.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"119\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"76\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<h3>Poole received his 1st degree black belt in 1986, under Tim Kirby, Billye Jackson and Raymond McCallum. Poole competed in the AOK and was a top ranked competitor in forms and fighting for many years as a junior competitor.<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole began working for and training with long time friend and kickboxing\\/MMA champion Guy Mezger in 1993. Poole began honing his boxing and kickboxing skills with Mezger, Billye Jackson, Santae Wilson Jr. and Coach Charles Brown and went on to win a national title in 1997, which earned a spot on the US National Kickboxing team.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole\\u2019s boxing experience comes from training with some of the best coaches in the business. Phil Sawyer and Olympic Boxing Bronze medalist Charles Brown have influenced Poole in his boxing training, as well as Alex Andrade, David Douglas and Michael Montoya.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole has several years of Muay Thai experience, training with Francisco Sanchez of New World Combat, as well as World Muay Thai champion and MMA veteran Pete Spratt and Muay Thai champion Jason House.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole\\u2019s Judo experience comes from training with Master Vince Tamura and Judo Black Belt Rico Castro.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole currently trains under the tutelage of 8th degree Brazilian Jiu Jitsu master, Carlos Machado, where he holds a brown belt and is a proud affiliate of Machado Jiu Jitsu. Poole has also trained with many talented Brazilian Jiu Jitsu black belts including Kenny McClure, Jeff Sawyer, Rico Castro and Taryn Douglas.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Poole has competed all over the United States and internationally in Europe, winning a KICK International title in 2004 along with many team karate titles from 1999-2004. Poole also fought for Team Texas in Chuck Norris\\u2019s televised fight league, The World Combat League.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p> Poole has parlayed his training and knowledge of martial arts into a successful career as a stuntman and fight\\/stunt coordinator for <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.imdb.com\\/name\\/nm1336664\\/\\\">television and film<\\/a>. Poole has performed and worked alongside some of the top names in the action world like Sylvester Stallone, Chuck Norris, Ben Affleck, Jason Statham and many others. Poole can be seen on popular television shows like The Walking Dead, Sons of Anarchy, From Dusk till Dawn and Marvel\\u2019s AGENTS of the SHIELD just to name a few and he has served as a stunt double, performing various feats of action for actors Sylvester Stallone, Frank Grillo and Jesse Metcalfe as well as many others. As a fight coordinator and stunt coordinator, Poole oversees and is in charge of action for feature films that can be seen on anywhere from Netflix to the big screen and television shows on network TV!<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:38:57', '2016-07-14 02:38:57', '07e33356-f5d5-4b86-ae38-e3ac3d5eb069'),
 ('152', '27', '3', '1', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Instructors\",\"slug\":\"instructors\",\"postDate\":1458873960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"28\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Instructors\",\"body\":\"<p>Our instructors have spent many years perfecting the martial arts craft and continue to go through extensive testing training and certifications to ensure that we are able to provide our students with the best care and instruction. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Here, we\\u2019re family and we truly enjoy what we do and we enjoy sharing that passion with others. Collectively we invest in each student, as we feel that their success is our success!<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"41\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"29\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"64\"],\"staffName\":\"Steve Sosa\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 7th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Steve Sosa has been an unstoppable, highly skilled martial artist for over 30 years. Master Sosa a 7th degree black belt in karate, trained by legendary martial artists such as Tim Kirby, Allen Steen, Ray McCallum, Billye Jackson, and Demetrius \\u201cThe Greek\\u201d Havanas - the original members of \\u201cTexas Blood \\u2018n\\u2019 Guts\\u201d karate in the Dallas area.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Master Sosa is a passionate trainer who has amassed several prestigious accolades in Martial Arts tournaments including \\u201cThe Golden Greek\\u201d which is the highest award given by the Amateur Organization of Karate. Master Sosa was also honored with the Positive Coaching Alliance\\u2019s Double-Goal Coaching Award, awarded to coaches who implement positive life skills, work ethic and drive into their students training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In 2010 Master Sosa started North Texas Martial Arts (NTMA), which ultimately joined Freddie Poole Martial Arts in 2015.<\\/p>\"}},\"65\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"99\"],\"staffName\":\"Vanny Boon\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, Saekson Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Master Vanny Boon is a certified 5th degree black belt skilled in various forms of martial arts including Taekwondo Do, Muay Thai, Brazilian Jiu jitsu and Boxing. Master Boon\\u2019s passion and experience for martial arts began when he started training at the age of 5 and spans over 25 years; Master Boon trained under Grand Master Hong, Master Freddie Poole and Muay Thai world champion Saekson Janjira.<\\/p>\"}},\"68\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"50\"],\"staffName\":\"Randy Stem\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, fitness trainer \",\"body\":\"<p>Randy Stem is a 5th degree black belt trained in Karate, Kickboxing, and Judo and currently in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. Randy studied under the teachings of Allen Steen, widely recognized as the \'Father of American Taekwondo\', and has over 45 years of experience mastering martial arts. Randy strongly encourages his students to build a firm foundation in martial arts early on by focusing on the development of basic fundamental motor skills and concepts.<\\/p>\"}},\"31\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"44\"],\"staffName\":\"Westin Poole\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Westin Poole\\u2019s love for karate kicked in as a kid when began training in martial arts at the age of 6. By 2009, Westin was a certified 1st degree black belt and has no plans of slowing down. He has been teaching for almost eight years and enjoys working with children. The mission behind his teaching is inspiring his students to reach their goals and see the benefits of their hard work.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"70\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"46\"],\"staffName\":\"Alex Garcia\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Alex Garcia is a 2nd degree black belt in Tae Kwon Do who gravitated towards the world of martial arts at the age of 4. Alex soon began training to develop and perfect his skills for martial arts and became a student at Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts at the age of 10. Within 2 years, Alex\\u2019s dedication transformed him into an avid competitor, in which Alex received several 1st place wins in state martial arts championships.<\\/p>\"}},\"72\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"100\"],\"staffName\":\"Mike Rose\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt \",\"body\":\"<p>Mike Rose has over 25 years of martial arts training, competition, and teaching experience in both Judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. Mike started training in Judo in 1992, when he received his black belt. In 1998, under the teachings of Greg Nelson, Mike began training in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and received his blue belt in 1999 and his black belt in 2009.<\\/p>\"}},\"71\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"45\"],\"staffName\":\"Nathan Bagby\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt, Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Nathanael \\u201cNathan\\u201d Bagby is a 3rd degree black belt and an accomplished Muay Thai fighter and instructor. Nathan first became interested and started training in martial arts at the age of 8, and in the past 25 years, has trained in Isshinryu Karate, Eskrima, Tae Kwon Do, American Kickboxing, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, Close Quarter Combat, Boxing, and Muay Thai. &nbsp;Nathan has gone on to compete in several amateur and professional kickboxing and Muay Thai bouts.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"30\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"62\"],\"staffName\":\"Jayda Clayton\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Jayda Clayton, a 2nd degree black belt, began her training in January 2007 at the ripe old age of 4. A prodigy of Master Steven Sosa, Jayda received her yellow and brown belts in 2007 and 2009, respectively. At age 7, Jayda became Master Sosa\\u2019s first and youngest student to receive her black belt. Jayda has competed in numerous local, state and national karate competitions and won over 60 trophies in sparring and kata competitions with over 40 of them being first place positions.<\\/p>\"}},\"66\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"48\"],\"staffName\":\"Johnny Rodriguez\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Professor Johnny Rodriguez is a highly skilled black belt in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu with over 20 years of training in several martial art forms including Kenpo karate, Aikido, Judo and Muay Thai. Professor Rodriguez teaches workshops, self-defense seminars, and has previously worked in law enforcement. &nbsp;Professor Rodriguez actively coaches students in preparation for BJJ tournaments and MMA bouts and still competes in many Brazilian jiu-jitsu tournaments.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"67\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"49\"],\"staffName\":\"Gerardo Mulas\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Certified Personal Trainer, Yoga\",\"body\":\"<p>Gerardo Mulas is a certified personal trainer, yoga and martial arts expert whose mission is educating students the benefits of fitness and health and wellness goals. Gerardo specializes in sports performance, weight loss, injury rehabilitation, stress relief, nutritional counseling and meal planning. Gerardo has over two decades of professional and collegiate athletics under his belt, along with extensive training in kickboxing, boxing and grappling.<\\/p>\"}},\"69\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"43\"],\"staffName\":\"Sovandy Om\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Sovandy Om is a 5th degree black belt, kickboxing fitness certified trainer and a FPMA student favorite. Master Om has trained extensively in Tae Kwon Do, MMA, Gymnastic, as well as Crossfit. Along with a passion for martial arts, Master Om has an even bigger passion for fitness. Master Om works tirelessly with helping the students execute proper technique to achieve the maximum benefits, as well as helping students reach and exceed their fitness goals.<\\/p>\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:39:38', '2016-07-14 02:39:38', 'f4dbce97-a166-4d10-aa0d-95784849dd99'),
 ('153', '16', '3', '1', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Dragons\",\"slug\":\"dragons\",\"postDate\":1458099960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"21\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Dragons (4 \\u2013 6 YO)\",\"body\":\"<p>Specifically designed for children four to six years of age where they will begin to learn the fundamental life skills such as self-discipline, focus, self-control respect, patience and confidence. Dragons will also learn fine motor skills such as strength, balance, flexibility, and coordination.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"130\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"22\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our Dragons program has a fun and energetic class format helps the young students develop skills that set them up for success in life. The structure of the Freddie Poole Dragons program is a key principle of success of the student as it\\u2019s a preparatory training program for the Junior Martial Arts Program<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"22\":\"Dragons (4 \\u2013 6 YO)\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:50:39', '2016-07-14 02:50:39', '0f43fdae-7514-48f9-a751-b98224195805'),
 ('154', '33', '3', '1', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Events\",\"slug\":\"events\",\"postDate\":1458879720,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"55\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Events\",\"body\":\"<p>We pride ourselves in offering superior service and training for parents and kids. Outside of our extensive martial arts programs offered at both of our Dallas locations, FPMA offers various extra personal services that are very educational, affordable and definitely FUN! From private birthday celebrations to women\\u2019s self-defense classes, there\\u2019s a special FPMA Extra for everyone.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"131\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"56\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Parent\\u2019s Nights Out\",\"body\":\"<p>Got a date night or hang out with the crew night planned and need somewhere to take the kiddos? Bring \\u2018em to FPMA for Parents Night Out (PNO). The PNO program is on specified Saturdays from 5-9pm and welcomes both FPMA students and non-members to join in on a night full of pizza, movies, prizes and fun. <strong><em>Oh, did we mention Nerf gun wars, too?<\\/em><\\/strong> <a href=\\\"\\/locations#entry:7:url\\\">Just give one of our locations a call<\\/a> for more information, pricing and dates for the next PNO.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}},\"57\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Birthday Parties\",\"body\":\"<p>Celebrate the birthday for your little martial artists Freddie Poole style! FPMA offers a personal experience with one of our many skilled instructors, ready to teach all of the little partiers some exciting new martial arts moves and put a unique spin on a birthday celebrations. Decorations, music and food are welcome. Interested in having your kid\\u2019s next birthday celebration at FPMA? <a href=\\\"tel:2143525425\\\">Give one of our locations a call<\\/a> for more information.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"58\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Special Events\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>FPMA is proud to announce our summer 2016 Karate Camp for kids.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Karate Camp is designed for children ages 4-11 and provides the perfect summer getaway for kids interested in learning more about the many forms of martial art. Give you kids the opportunity to learn more about boosting leadership and teamwork skills, building and improving self confidence, self defense techniques, bully awareness as well as fun martial arts games and drills. Choose from 2 summer camp sessions only a $25 deposit required to reserve a spot. Reach out to a FPMA location for more details.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"77\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Women\\u2019s Self Defense Seminars\",\"body\":\"<p>Safety for our members is a major priority for us. FPMA offers self-defense classes for women to learn how to protect themselves and their loved ones from unexpected attacks. Join FPMA for one of our Women\\u2019s Self Defense Seminars in partnership with Not Dead Yet Apparel. Come get hands-on training as we demonstrate various self-defense techniques, learn empowering safety awareness and practices. Attendance is always free, but we accept donations of $25 or more to benefit a designated local non-profit organization. Take the first step by contacting one of our locations for more information.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"78\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Personal Training \",\"body\":\"<p>For the member who wants to learn the valuable techniques of martial arts outside of a group setting, FPMA offers specialized one-on-one training sessions. Members get individually structured personal instruction from one of our certified martial arts trainers. Training sessions are customized to benefit each student in any skill level, from a novice student wanting a more personal experience or an advanced student preparing for competition. <a href=\\\"\\/contact-us#entry:32:url\\\">Contact one of our two Dallas locations<\\/a> for more details.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:51:27', '2016-07-14 02:51:27', 'b0afbf1b-e5d4-4c0d-ae25-41debf15409d'),
 ('155', '81', '3', '1', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"slug\":\"brazilian-jiu-jitsu\",\"postDate\":1465960800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"82\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu: (7 to 12-year-old + Adults)&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The sport of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu can be quite complex. Our intro program helps break down all the essential concepts of the sport making it much easier to pick up for anybody. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial arts is a proud affiliate of the Carlos Machado BJJ association and network. Carlos Machado is nephew to one of the founders of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, late master Carlos Gracie. Carlos is determined to keep the legacy going through teaching and partnering with others including our very own, Freddie Poole.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"40\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"83\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our classes are curriculum oriented, providing a fast paced yet easy approach to learning Brazilian Jiu Jitsu for children (7-12 years of age) and adults. Students achieve great results in a short amount of time learning realistic skills great for both self-defense and increasing fitness and stamina. Students also learn strategies for advancing in rank after completing time and skill requirements, all in a fun and safe environment.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}},\"84\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kids BJJ Program\",\"body\":\"<p>The FPMA Brazilian Jiu Jitsu kids program is the perfect tool to change your child\\u2019s life forever. Lessons learned both on and off the mat will instill in them a confidence and self-belief that will continue with them throughout their lives. Plus, it\\u2019s FUN! FPMA stands firm on our anti-bullying policies, which have been reverse engineered to safely and effectively repel any aggressor, with truly phenomenal results.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Overall, the Kids BBJ program is designed to develop a sense of discipline, determination, leadership, commitment, responsibility, good sportsmanship and confidence into our future leaders<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"85\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Adults BJJ Fundamentals\",\"body\":\"<p>FPMA BJJ Fundamentals Program is designed to teach the overall self-defense strategy of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. The class begins with a pre-workout involving many body weight exercises and it will teach you the basics, from learning how to fall, to clinching, taking down and successfully setting up and applying a submission hold as well as various escapes. We provide a detailed instruction in wrestling, judo, and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, as they are all relevant to mastership. The class ends with positional training that helps students focus on the lesson of the week and get a feel for live training. Through repetition techniques, your training will slowly prepare you to begin drilling at a full resistance.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"22\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:55:56', '2016-07-14 02:55:56', 'f607edde-3e5f-485b-bee3-bc053075a35c'),
 ('156', '128', '3', '1', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"FPMA\",\"slug\":\"about-us-1\",\"postDate\":1468463520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"129\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"FPMA\",\"body\":\"<p>Since opening its doors in 2004, Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has been impacting thousands of lives in the community. Our friendly staff looks forward each day to helping our students achieve their goals.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Although standards are set high, each student at FPMA is evaluated on an individual basis to ensure progression on their own timeline. This approach ensures students achieve and earn rank on their own merit. We encourage our students to trust the process and enjoy it. Earning a black belt at FPMA is a once in a lifetime experience! The dedicated team of instructors at FPMA have taken their experience of martial arts and created a well-rounded training system for all ages. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts is the most balanced martial arts training system, combining traditional training elements with practical real world application. By integrating both of these elements into one system, one can truly train in mixed martial arts.\",\"body\":\"\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:57:12', '2016-07-14 02:57:12', '4ad23c57-2bdf-48c5-99aa-d81aabe3e25e'),
 ('157', '128', '3', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"FPMA\",\"slug\":\"about-us-1\",\"postDate\":1468463520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"129\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"FPMA\",\"body\":\"<p>Since opening its doors in 2004, Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has been impacting thousands of lives in the community. Our friendly staff looks forward each day to helping our students achieve their goals.<br><\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Although standards are set high, each student at FPMA is evaluated on an individual basis to ensure progression on their own timeline. This approach ensures students achieve and earn rank on their own merit. We encourage our students to trust the process and enjoy it. Earning a black belt at FPMA is a once in a lifetime experience! The dedicated team of instructors at FPMA have taken their experience of martial arts and created a well-rounded training system for all ages. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts is the most balanced martial arts training system, combining traditional training elements with practical real world application. By integrating both of these elements into one system, one can truly train in mixed martial arts.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-14 02:57:38', '2016-07-14 02:57:38', '5a895bac-98ae-4a89-91c3-ae26ec65fb0f'),
